’Щ@e8bd067c8668d606d62b78ad74bf92b031f74c08d4b06a27f7406579d2807a17Ъ}Title: title: polars str-lengths
Path: Examples
Content:
Returns string lengths for a column
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[a]; [a] [ab] [abc]] | polars into-df | polars select (polars col a | polars str-lengths) | polars collect
